<div class="container-users">
  <div class="flex-profil">
    <div class="carte-container">
      <div class="carte-profil">
        <h5 class="carte-title"><%= @user.username %></h5>
        <% if @user.trader == true %>
          <%= @user.trader_score %>
        <% end %>
        <% if @user.player == true %>
          <%= @user.player_score %>
        <% end %>
          <%= @user.trust_score %>
        <div class="carte-image">
          <% if @user.image%>
            <%= cl_image_tag @user.image.key, width: '100%', height: '257px'%>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="carte-body">
          <div>
            <% if @user_games == 'Yu-gi-Oh'%>
              <h6>Duelliste</h6>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div>
          <%# <%= link_to 'Modifier mon profil', edit_user_path(@user), class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          <%= link_to 'Discuter', chatroom_path(@user), class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card description-profil">
      <h2 class="card-header">Description</h2>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="card-text">
            <%= @user.description %>
        </p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="card-header">Historique des duels</h2>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="card-text">
            "Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium,
            totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta
            sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia
            consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui
            dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit, sed quia non numquam eius modi tempora
            incidunt ut labore et
        </p>
        <%= link_to 'Modifier mon profil', edit_user_path(@user), class: "btn btn-primary"  %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
